{"tid":800889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[延長車程] 九巴招標開發新收費系統 畀車錢有得「嘟」信用卡兼掃二維碼","createTime":"2018-08-31T08:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T08:21:15.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c854b8693ebcad5663929a3e1699a5b22fb3cd66","tid":800889,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"搭巴士除了「嘟」八達通外，將有更多選擇，九巴正式招標開發新電子收費系統，新系統將可使用智能信用卡及<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>手機二維碼（QR CODE）</strong></span>繳付車費。<br />\n<br />\n九巴在招標通告指出，九巴及龍運巴士計劃開發新電子收費系統，令乘客除了用現金及八達通支付車費外，有更多選擇。新系統將可使用非接觸EMV智能信用卡，及二維碼（QR CODE）繳付車費。入標者須為金管局認可承辦商，新系統須符合運輸署的車費指引。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵較早前亦招標開發二維碼（QR CODE）收費系統，有報道指Alipay及WeChat Pay等都有意入標。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但有不少網民均擔心，掃描二維碼及確認所需時間比使用八達通長，擔心會造成阻塞</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58629270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58629270&d=0%2F%2Bsm2iTreXJo34rCNGgVu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=569a3a94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58629270&h=e6177c9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58629270</a>"},{"pid":"883d5378182c135a07c7cfabeeca1d3461938b0c","tid":800889,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"班女人拍八達通都要拍幾廿次先OK，再用埋QR Code隨時一個鐘車程變個半鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dec693e854dccc4e2de3163cdb005d92a97964","tid":800889,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:21:15.000Z","msg":"如果有日乜鳩支那寶/We柒Pay Update 完瘋狂彈APP,<br />\n咁果日啲巴士仲開唔開到車?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}